title: Formula 1 2013 Italian Qualifying
description:
This is the full broadcast from BBC and small file size but good quality for those who have slow internet, capper is DoctorDolittle.


Suzi Perry presents coverage from the Autodromo Nazionale Monza (Start-time 1.00pm), as the drivers battle for pole position in the 12th round of the season. Lewis Hamilton qualified fastest here last year with his then team-mate Jenson Button joining him on the front of the grid. Button's McLaren has struggled for pace this season, but Hamilton will be looking for another impressive qualifying performance in his Mercedes. Commentary by Ben Edwards and David Coulthard.
